item.description: Come climb, socialize and meet new people! The gym is run non-profit with donations welcome. A signed waiver is required. All level climbers are welcome. Some gear available, so don't worry if you are a beginner, I can teach you!
item.how_to_find_us: One and half miles down Scruton Pond Rd is #194 Maroon ranch w/ large barn in back. Come in driveway or park out front. Come out back through fence and entrance is right there.
item.name: The NH Rock Climbing February Meetup
